<title>THE CITY OF GOLD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thihna luiguom khelah khawpi hawihtak a um,
 A lopi zie gentheih guollouh chuh;
 Zie chun nitum ngeilo thingnah leh pulh ngeilo,
 Zie sana khawpi hawih tak achun.

[V2]
 Ziechun nitum ngeilo,
 Thingnah le pulh ngeilo;
 Mi ginum te'n a Hukdampau mel chuh mu'n au,
 Zie sana khawpi hawih taka chun.

[V3]
 2. Ziechun Lalpen, I Tanpau I hehpih Lalpa,
 Ginum ten kipak takin mu'n au;
 Mi diktat te aksi guolin vak zing ta'n au,
 Zie sana khawpi hawih tak achun.

[V4]
 3. Thagau mang Kross bula I puihkhawm teu cheng chuh,
 Belam No huongsunga I puih cheng
 I Lallukhuk zemhawih dingteu chuh hung hi'n au,
 Zie sana khawpi hawih tak achun.</lyrics>
</song>